name: I Used To Think I Was ...
description:
Bricaffi

The combination of brick walls and graffiti with memorable quotes or images make up this
wonderful collection.

Bricks
These 1:12th brick slips are hand made and cast from reconstituted stone, which makes these realistic minis, brick walls.

Each slip measures approx 19mm x 5.5mm x 2mm thick. These come in weathered grey, Grey, Weathered Red, Tudor Red, and Antique Red

Frame
Chunky photo frame in white, black and oak with mount. Image size with mount 8inx6in and frame is 12inx10in.
Suitable to hang. Frame width 2cm.

name: Lemon
description:
ekoc upcycling

This exciting range takes an everyday object of the humble can and turns in into a fun piece of artwork. For example one can of fanta orange makes one ekoc orange can picture.

Upcycling
Is the process of converting waste materials or useless products into new materials or products of better quality or a higher environmental value.

Cans
330ml Aluminium can, with holes with a diameter of 6Â±0.5 mm, are punched out.

Frame
Deep box frame in black or white with mount. Image size with mount 7inx7in and frame is 8inx8in.
Suitable to hang. Frame width 2cm.

name: Matchstick-Colour
description:
skull

A fun use of matchsticks, which will make your eyes heart go up in flames for these tactile
